{
  "stem": "9701.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it gave all the dos and don'ts, that you can't come and visit, that efforts to release the men would be futile, how often you can write, how much you can write, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Once we knew where the men were, where my father was, where all the other men were, my mother decided to go to the Gestapo office, that's G-E-S-T-A-P-O, that's the Nazi secret police office which was in Karlsruhe, that's K-A-R-L-S-R-U-H-E, a town that was quite some distance from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother left early in the morning by train and came back late at night by train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember begging my mother not to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, you know, because if they keep you, I won't have a mother and I won't have a father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my mother said, you want your father and all the others to come home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I have to go and see if there's anything that I can do to bring that about.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so you must let me go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so reluctantly I let her go and lived in fear until she came back late at night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she went every day and came back with no information though, until the Monday of the fourth week after the men and boys had been arrested.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she was told that morning that if-- that my father would come back that week.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But if he's not back by Friday, he will never come back anymore because he's no longer alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the first few men arrived back on that very day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we heard about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we visited them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I was not really allowed to remain in the room when conversation took place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My mother said, you're still too young.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
